%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4b89517e-0212-4930-a2cd-d04b1276d48a_552x308.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!SY74!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4b89517e-0212-4930-a2cd-d04b1276d48a_552x308.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><div class="pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset"><button tabindex="0" type="button" class="pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image"><svg role="img" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="var(--color-fg-primary)" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g><title></title><path d="M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882"></path></g></svg></button><button tabindex="0" type="button" class="pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2"><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></button></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p><strong>19: </strong>In response to my crime statistics <a href="https://www.astralcodexten.com/p/record-low-crime-rates-are-real-not">post</a>, Theodidactus <a href="https://broodingomnipresence.substack.com/p/how-many-crimes-are-there-and-why">discusses the impossibility of truly defining and numbering crimes</a> (eg did Sam Bankman-Fried commit one crime, a handful of different crimes, or [total number of FTX customers] crimes?) Hopefully you can predict my response, which is that all concepts <a href="https://slatestarcodex.com/2014/08/14/beware-isolated-demands-for-rigor/">become </a>unmanageable when you zoom in too far and prudence tells us how far we should zoom at any given moment.</p><p><strong>20: </strong>California&#8217;s AI safety law may incidentally create whistleblower protections for AI company employees in California (h/t <a href="https://x.com/Thomas_Woodside/status/2025933437828280710">@Thomas_Woodside</a>):</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-img" target="_blank" href="https://x.com/Thomas_Woodside/status/2025933437828280710" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!c54V!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcda04303-bb69-4335-9120-e6abf04000f0_587x620.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!c54V!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcda04303-bb69-4335-9120-e6abf04000f0_587x620.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!c54V!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcda04303-bb69-4335-9120-e6abf04000f0_587x620.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!c54V!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcda04303-bb69-4335-9120-e6abf04000f0_587x620.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!c54V!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media